data.description: Beautifully updated, turnkey home in sought-after Paddlers Cove.  2 story foyer with board and batten welcomes you into the home.  Office with French doors makes working from home a breeze.  Renovated living room with shiplap over an electric fireplace, board & batten accents, and crown molding.  Primary bedroom on main with a spacious bathroom, separate water closet, and WIC.  Large bonus room upstairs with 3 bedrooms gives everyone space to move around.  Extended paver stone patio with privacy wall, pergola, fire pit, outdoor kitchen with natural gas line plumbed and fenced backyard.  Corner lot allows extra parking for guests.  Community pool, sidewalks throughout, walking distance to CSD Community YMCA & Crowders Creek Elementary.  Minutes away from Lake Wylie!
